description: A collection of circles in a small bean-shaped formation above a larger  almond-shaped formation of circles with a triangular formation extending outwards from the right side of the almond-shaped formation. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a yellowish-orange triangle in the center of the bean-shaped formation and a longer, thinner yellowish-orange triangle on the right side of the triangular formaiton.
